reviews.text: I was the only customer at 4:20 am ... I had to wait 20 min for my lamb & chips!  I asked for medium spicy BUT I got SUPER hot! :(  The staff was indifferent & distracted!  The Lamb was all burnt-leftovers! Not nice ...
Wide selection and fairly good quality, especially for the price point. Generally space available and quick table turnover. For place for a late night bite.
Authentic chicken Sharwama. A bit salty compared to what I ate in Qatar but definitely well done. Service is quick.
Nice place to get some Indian food. Value for money
Since, my visit to Hong Kong it's the best place to get Indian food....must go.....I like it's masala chai as well. Try channa masala and rice,  falafel roll, paneer Tikka masala as well

reviews.text:
睇 Show 前恩物。地點近，價位好，無乜人
味道正宗
기대를 많이 하고 가진 않았는데 상상초월...진짜 맛있어서 깜짝 놀란다. 홍콩에서 제일 맛있다. 내일 아침에 또 먹으러 갈거임!!! 한국가도 계속 생각날 것 같아서 조금 무섭다. 너무 짜고 느끼한 홍콩 현지 음식에 지쳤다면 적당히 자극적인 이 식당을 적극 추천한다. 저 치킨라이스를 드셔보시길.
